From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MC20018 <winme2001@outlook.com>
Date: Mon, 8 Jun 2026 00:00:12 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Expand Fand event hooks

Add vanilla hook points for world saves, weather changes, chunk lifecycle, entity lifecycle, entity teleports, explosions, player item/state events, game mode changes, kicks, and low-level block change/physics events.

Keep patched code thin by routing all API wrapping and listener failure handling through Fand server bridge classes.

diff --git a/net/minecraft/server/MinecraftServer.java b/net/minecraft/server/MinecraftServer.java
